wwpLeosExtLagMIB.name: wwpLeosExtLagMIB
wwpLeosExtLagMIB.contactinfo: Mib Meister 115 North Sullivan Road Spokane Valley, WA 99037 USA Phone: +1 509 242 9000 Email: support@ciena.com
wwpLeosExtLagMIB.description: This MIB module is an extension to the IEEE8023-LAG-mib. This MIB defines the managed objects for the creation and deletion of Aggregators.

wwpLeosMaxLags.name: wwpLeosMaxLags
wwpLeosMaxLags.description: The maximum number of aggregators that this device supports.

wwpLeosNumLags.name: wwpLeosNumLags
wwpLeosNumLags.description: The current number of LAGs that are configured in this device.

wwpLeosExtLagTable.name: wwpLeosExtLagTable
wwpLeosExtLagTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing all the aggregators.

wwpLeosExtLagEntry.name: wwpLeosExtLagEntry
wwpLeosExtLagEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the wwpLeosExtLagTable.

wwpLeosExtAggId.name: wwpLeosExtAggId
wwpLeosExtAggId.description: Object which specifies a unique entry in the wwpLeosExtLagTable. A management station wishing to create a LAG should use a pseudo-random value for this object when creating an instance of a wwpLeosExtLagEntry.

wwpLeosExtAggName.name: wwpLeosExtAggName
wwpLeosExtAggName.description: The name assigned to this Lag by the Management station. This object can only be set while creating LAG. It is not allowed to rename the LAG name once it is created.

wwpLeosExtAggIndex.name: wwpLeosExtAggIndex
wwpLeosExtAggIndex.description: The unique identifier allocated to this Aggregator by the local System. This attribute identifies an Aggregator instance among the subordinate managed objects of the containing object. This value is read-only. This object refer to the dot3adAggIndex in the IEEE-8023-LAG-MIB.

wwpLeosExtAggStatus.name: wwpLeosExtAggStatus
wwpLeosExtAggStatus.description: Used to manage the creation and deletion of the conceptual rows in this table. To create a row in this table, a manager must set this object to 'createAndGo'. To disable the aggregator, a management should set this object to 'notInService'.

wwpLeosExtAggMode.name: wwpLeosExtAggMode
wwpLeosExtAggMode.description: This object specifies the mode in which given aggregation is operating.

wwpLeosExtLagProtectionRevertState.name: wwpLeosExtLagProtectionRevertState
wwpLeosExtLagProtectionRevertState.description: This object specifies that if the primary port goes from operationally disabled to operationally enabled it shall become active, and one of the secondary ports shall become backup if this MIB object is set to 'on' and the wwpLeosLagProtectionRevertTimer timer expires.

wwpLeosExtLagProtectionRevertTimer.name: wwpLeosExtLagProtectionRevertTimer
wwpLeosExtLagProtectionRevertTimer.description: This object specifies the revert protection timer value.

wwpLeosExtAggHashMode.name: wwpLeosExtAggHashMode
wwpLeosExtAggHashMode.description: This object specifies the hash mode used by the aggregation for known unicast frames.

wwpLeosExtLagProtectionMode.name: wwpLeosExtLagProtectionMode
wwpLeosExtLagProtectionMode.description: This object specifies the LACP protection-mode in which given aggregation is operating.

wwpLeosLagModeTable.name: wwpLeosLagModeTable
wwpLeosLagModeTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the modes of aggregation on each port.

wwpLeosLagModeEntry.name: wwpLeosLagModeEntry
wwpLeosLagModeEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the wwpLeosLagModeTable.

wwpLeosLagPhyPortId.name: wwpLeosLagPhyPortId
wwpLeosLagPhyPortId.description: This object specifies the physical port number. It is also used as index in the table.

wwpLeosLagAdminMode.name: wwpLeosLagAdminMode
wwpLeosLagAdminMode.description: This object specifies the administrative mode in which given port is operating.

wwpLeosLagOperMode.name: wwpLeosLagOperMode
wwpLeosLagOperMode.description: This object specifies the operation mode in which given port is operating.

wwpLeosLagProtectionTable.name: wwpLeosLagProtectionTable
wwpLeosLagProtectionTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing the protection ports for each aggregation.

wwpLeosLagProtectionEntry.name: wwpLeosLagProtectionEntry
wwpLeosLagProtectionEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the wwpLeosLagProtectionTable.

wwpLeosLagProtectionPort.name: wwpLeosLagProtectionPort
wwpLeosLagProtectionPort.description: This object specifies the protection port number. It is also used as index in the table.

wwpLeosLagProtectionRowStatus.name: wwpLeosLagProtectionRowStatus
wwpLeosLagProtectionRowStatus.description: Used to manage the creation and deletion of the conceptual rows in this table. To create a row in this table, a manager must set this object to 'createAndGo'. To delete entry set this object to 'destroy'.

wwpLeosExtAggFloodHashMode.name: wwpLeosExtAggFloodHashMode
wwpLeosExtAggFloodHashMode.description: This object specifies the aggregation hash mode used by unknown unicast, multicast and broadcast frames for all aggregation ports in the system.
